### ===========================================================================
### PROJECT MEMBER MODULE - HTTP CLIENT TEST
### ===========================================================================

@baseUrl   = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token     = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJtaW5nMTgzODBAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3OTc0MjI4LCJleHAiOjE3NzgwNjA2MjgsInJvbGUiOlsiUk9MRV9VU0VSIl19.1nFlL8nU3uKK473r7gGoL4FtE2gLelN2YRCjJA_sgKw
@projectId = 1
@userId    = 7

### ===========================================================================
### 1. GET - Lấy danh sách member
### ===========================================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members?page=0&size=20
Authorization: {{token}}
 
### ===========================================================================
### 2. GET - Filter theo role
### ===========================================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members?role=Admin&page=0&size=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### ===========================================================================
### 3. GET - Thống kê member theo role
### ===========================================================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/statistic
Authorization: {{token}}

### ===========================================================================
### 4. POST - Mời MEMBER (ADMIN hoặc LEAD thực hiện)
### ===========================================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "role": "Member"
}

### ===========================================================================
### 5. POST - Mời LEAD (chỉ ADMIN thực hiện)
### ===========================================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "role": "Lead"
}


### 6. POST - Mời ADMIN (chỉ ADMIN thực hiện)

POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "role": "Admin"
}

### ===========================================================================
### 7. PATCH - Đổi role thành viên (chỉ ADMIN)
### ===========================================================================

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{userId}}/role
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Lead"
}

### ===========================================================================
### 8. DELETE - Kick thành viên
### ===========================================================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{userId}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### ===========================================================================
### 9. DELETE - Tự rời dự án
### ===========================================================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/leave
Authorization: {{token}}

### ===========================================================================
### EDGE CASES
### ===========================================================================

### EC-1: userId null -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": null,
  "role": "Member"
}

### EC-2: Role không hợp lệ -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "role": "INVALID_ROLE"
}

### EC-3: Mời user đã là member -> 409 Conflict
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 12,
  "role": "Member"
}

### EC-4: LEAD mời ADMIN -> 403 Forbidden
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "role": "Admin"
}

### EC-5: MEMBER đổi role -> 403 Forbidden
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{userId}}/role
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Viewer"
}

### EC-6: ADMIN tự hạ role mình -> 403 Forbidden
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/4/role
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Member"
}

### EC-7: ADMIN duy nhất leave -> 403 Forbidden
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/leave
Authorization: {{token}}

### EC-8: Tự kick chính mình -> 400 Bad Request
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/4
Authorization: {{token}}

### EC-9: LEAD kick ADMIN -> 403 Forbidden
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/4
Authorization: {{token}}

### EC-10: Project không tồn tại -> 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/99999/members
Authorization: {{token}}

### EC-11: Không có token -> 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members